This article establishes an enterprise belief function in industrial clusters based on the analysis of the research about belief, and the analysis framework of industrial clusters. It also analyzes the mechanism that endogenous variables act on enterprise belief function. Then take the automobile industrial clusters in Yuhuan city, Zhejiang province for example, use these outcomes to do some compared application analysis on enterprise belief function of different levels. At last, we get the conclusion as follow. The belief level of enterprise is constrained by many factors, including the overall level of industrial clusters, enterprise transaction frequency, strategy selections, network positions, quantities of relationship, entrepreneurâ€™s credit and time dimension. The high belief level is able to improve enterprise competitive advantage, and then increases enterprise loyalty degree in industrial clusters.